					>
						5 days · 7 lectures
					</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── ABOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="mb-14">
		<p class="leading-relaxed">
			A five-day intensive research workshop bringing together Master's and PhD students from Japan
